{"tid":264473,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"6日5夜 獨遊高雄有咩玩？","createTime":"2017-05-31T00:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T03:45:24.000Z","uid":105100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"473a3c8f6b4affbe4a6f019eff2bf4d3f7a09329","tid":264473,"uid":105100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:08:25.000Z","msg":"一個人去高雄6日好似有啲多又悶 <br />\n諗緊去唔去埋墾丁好？去幾多日先好？"},{"pid":"04a6708ac1dc83b9db576a619b7a8882c02275a5","tid":264473,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人去高雄6日好似有啲多又悶 <br />\n諗緊去唔去埋墾丁好？去幾多日先好？</blockquote><br />\n去，風景好"},{"pid":"54fd645513c5a44349b58911da7aa95fca5ea0c7","tid":264473,"uid":105100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個人去高雄6日好似有啲多又悶 <br />\n諗緊去唔去埋墾丁好？去幾多日先好？</blockquote><br />\n去，風景好</blockquote><br />\n但去幾多日好4日3夜係墾丁？<br />\n因為我張機票去高雄個程係夜晚10點幾先到<br />\n走個程就中午2點幾機翻香港。<br />\n所以去高雄先再去墾丁？"},{"pid":"c06b192058dd163f8fb17ba53336f7151e8a4d30","tid":264473,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:24:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個人去高雄6日好似有啲多又悶 <br />\n諗緊去唔去埋墾丁好？去幾多日先好？</blockquote><br />\n去，風景好</blockquote><br />\n但去幾多日好4日3夜係墾丁？<br />\n因為我張機票去高雄個程係夜晚10點幾先到<br />\n走個程就中午2點幾機翻香港。<br />\n所以去高雄先再去墾丁？</blockquote><br />\n墾丁3日內夠玩，主要睇多過玩，而我上次住墾丁大街後面既靜觀行館"},{"pid":"4a2f61f905c8ceef1e4fb2cd128b5aa6f75c9d57","tid":264473,"uid":79389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"高雄點玩到咁耐 悶死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096764bf2a6c45e5aefbb203209b696cf67bcc26","tid":264473,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:27:34.000Z","msg":"你一個人應該都偏向唔會玩D咩樂園，到墾丁租架電單車會有地圖仔俾你，跟住路線去就得，好舒服"},{"pid":"b75b3d3ce8abdd8a5860901b5a8da0252eb3b412","tid":264473,"uid":105100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你一個人應該都偏向唔會玩D咩樂園，到墾丁租架電單車會有地圖仔俾你，跟住路線去就得，好舒服</blockquote><br />\n真架？好想去墾丁玩浮潛個啲"},{"pid":"280964b96a64378c51f2f32b05676ba86de28fe7","tid":264473,"uid":105100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高雄點玩到咁耐 悶死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原本就唔係自己一個人去嘅係同朋友去 但買左機票之後臨時有事又去唔到 所以就變左自己一個人去 高雄真係好悶上網睇😅"},{"pid":"3488023fabec52fc69a4862d1149e557c798131f","tid":264473,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:11:58.000Z","msg":"search 梵高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2301e480a3097f61ff1f51eaa724bebcd965e096","tid":264473,"uid":23757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T13:15:44.000Z","msg":"可以去下台南<br />\n懇丁一個人就唔好去啦 交通唔方便 冇可能包車<br />\n我遲啲都6日5夜高雄 有1日去台南<br />\n依家係驚會唔會落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c64fd374f16d33e9b574faca70e5e9c5aa10e1e","tid":264473,"uid":115856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"你幾時去高雄？"},{"pid":"f7a6ca4a9abdc1fac82c78b8a29a0a3b76805ffc","tid":264473,"uid":15358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"人在高雄 巴打幾時到？"},{"pid":"6cf037696d18c74c81a9727a961a94eef4a3a042","tid":264473,"uid":105100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以去下台南<br />\n懇丁一個人就唔好去啦 交通唔方便 冇可能包車<br />\n我遲啲都6日5夜高雄 有1日去台南<br />\n依家係驚會唔會落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該唔會掛 要check清楚天氣先得"},{"pid":"ec122efa50e251380e094847491947d3754ec77f","tid":264473,"uid":105100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你幾時去高雄？</blockquote><br />\n7月頭"},{"pid":"eacd241265a3b8ed400d749a800bbcc3bb760dc0","tid":264473,"uid":6208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"我同班friend都係去六日啊 不過係2日高雄 2日澎湖 2日墾丁 淨係高雄真係冇咩玩 如果你有興趣可以去下勃二藝術特區"},{"pid":"52ffb8cb9e33599bf3206a305ddf5b6a67c384ea","tid":264473,"uid":38559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"想浮潛小琉球都有，不過入去嘅交通費就貴d，我係六合夜市出發飛的去東港碼頭單程6xxTWD，再搭船入去來回410twd，去嘅話我建議你搭捷運到東港站，再搵的士，咁就平d。<br />\n<br />\n東港仲有魚生食，再加上有d特色手信，唔洗次次都買鳳梨酥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旗津都係個好地方，租架電動車輕鬆去齊咁多個景點"},{"pid":"f8b883ecc1d9e6786d902eb37460d6a5aa0233cb","tid":264473,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"舊年聖誕墾丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6zo7hrvt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6zo7hrvt&h=b5fc0e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i8uk79nw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi8uk79nw&h=0db5ce40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nol94qut\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnol94qut&h=bf40dd82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0f3z4y1v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0f3z4y1v&h=884dffac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v2hsnj4m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv2hsnj4m&h=a4185790&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d6c73ad8bbf161a975839bdaae72cf38e2907ce","tid":264473,"uid":39878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人在高雄 巴打幾時到？</blockquote><br />\n巴打走左未 我依家獨遊緊"},{"pid":"c09b3a7161d743bc4d2320ac888d9f903d018e8b","tid":264473,"uid":44220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"Tom's world"},{"pid":"bd0e46bdba719caa703da355f42207